      "act": "COLD OPEN",
      "estimated_duration_s": 10,
      "narration_text": "This is Liam, in for Bear. Two protons, one electron, and a choice that looks almost cosmetic: add two one-s orbitals, or subtract them. One choice can bind. The other cannot.",
